<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>물품 관리</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                    <i data-lucide="package" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">물품 관리</h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">병원 내 의료소모품 및 비품 재고를 관리합니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/item-manager/form" class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="plus" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                물품 등록
            </a>
        </div>

        <form action="/item-manager/list" method="GET" class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-2 md:pb-0 w-full md:w-auto">
                <button type="submit" name="category" value="ALL" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-indigo-600 text-white">전체</button>
                <button type="submit" name="category" value="MEDICAL" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200">의료소모품</button>
                <button type="submit" name="category" value="DRUG" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200">의약품</button>
                <button type="submit" name="category" value="OFFICE" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors whitespace-nowrap bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200">사무용품</button>
            </div>
            <div class="relative w-full md:w-64">
                <i data-lucide="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                <input type="text" name="keyword" value="" placeholder="물품명 검색..." class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none text-sm"/>
            </div>
        </form>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                <thead>
                    <tr class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">물품명</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium">카테고리</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium text-right">현재 재고</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium text-right">최소 수량</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium text-center">상태</th>
                        <th class="p-4 font-medium text-right">관리</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
                    <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">알코올 솜</td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-medium">의료소모품</span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm font-bold text-right text-slate-800">
                            50 개
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-500 text-right">
                            10 개
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-center">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800">
                                정상
                            </span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="p-4 text-right">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2">
                                <a href="/item-manager/form/1" class="p-1.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50 rounded-md transition-colors inline-block">
                                    <i data-lucide="edit-2" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                                </a>
                                <form action="/item-manager/delete" method="POST" class="inline" onsubmit="return confirm('정말 삭제하시겠습니까?');">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="itemId" value="1">
                                    <button type="submit" class="p-1.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50 rounded-md transition-colors">
                                        <i data-lucide="trash-2" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
            <nav class="flex gap-2"><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded">1</span></nav>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>